  "body": "<p>The July kits are available now at Studio Calico. I really enjoyed working with these colors and fun elements. This month I got the main scrapbook kit, the Jennifer Add-on, the Project Life kit, and Winona.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/1cf591efb24c3cc7.jpg?v=1782538322\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"20b-yes-555x600.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/2ce3fda39821d4c5.jpg?v=1782538325\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"20c-maddie_on_things-555x600.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7e723952c14077d3.jpg?v=1782538327\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20d-love_my_job-562x600.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7be2071d00a4e887.jpg?v=1782538330\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20e-lisbon-554x600.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/fd8d7035a1a9d208.jpg?v=1782538333\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20f-home-554x600.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/246aba7220cbfb0f.jpg?v=1782538336\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20g-going_places_with_you-564x600.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/9cad80d8f29de518.jpg?v=1782538338\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>We designed an exclusive stamp set for the Scrapbook kit. It's the only place you can get it! Shop for all the Studio Calico Valley High kits and check out all the creative team work here.</p><p>SPECIAL OFFER! NEW SUBSCRIBERS can get $5 off each kit by using the following codes:</p><ul><li><p>Valley High scrapbook subscription:  SCRAPBOOKVALLEY</p></li><li><p>Valley High card subscription:  CARDVALLEY</p></li><li><p>Valley High Project Life subscription:  PLVALLEY</p></li></ul><p>But hurry, coupon codes expire June 30th at midnight EST.</p><p>******************************************************************</p><p>For my layout using the Scrapbook Main kit only, I thought I would show you how it came together.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"20h-DSC_04141-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/d262061b8dc395e6.jpg?v=1782538341\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20i-DSC_0415-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/0cc6c5186b7c2c58.jpg?v=1782538344\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20j-DSC_04161-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/be75ea4192dae692.jpg?v=1782538347\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20k-DSC_0417-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/aee4b6bb0429216d.jpg?v=1782538349\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20l-DSC_04181-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/22f0b01f471a5769.jpg?v=1782538352\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20m-DSC_0419-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/0af80b84acdba4a0.jpg?v=1782538355\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20n-DSC_04201-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/cfb09e6a52b49fc2.jpg?v=1782538357\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20o-DSC_0421-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/53b61369432edf7b.jpg?v=1782538361\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20p-25_weeks-552x600.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/b772268ad9c0bf9c.jpg?v=1782538363\"/>"
